page1.title: About Me
page1.content: 👋🏻 I’m Aniket, an engineer who loves to tinker. . 🔨 I am a Machine Learning Engineer at Accenture. I am working on search for healthcare enterprises. I am also into web development, actively learning and building apps. In the past, I have integrated features based on ML into web apps built using react. I have interests in NLP and next generation web apps. Currently, I am learning Graph ML and its applications. . 🧬 Besides day to day work, I read a lot. Currently, I am reading 📚 Susan Cain’s Quiet and Andre Agassi’s Open. . 💸 I love discussing about technology, cryptocurrency, investing or any random facts and stories. . ✉️ You can email me or reach out to me on twitter or linkedin .
